{"tid":349190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本瘋狂院長改造成醫院 令人樂而忘返","createTime":"2017-08-06T11:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T13:58:48.000Z","uid":55981,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db2f61eed478bb2314274f6bdc448b1db336fef1","tid":349190,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T11:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaaXrQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaaXrQ.jpg&h=192269c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這是醫院不是動物園這是醫院不是動物園這是醫院不是動物園這是動物園（咦？）我要是來這裡檢查絕對會懷疑自己走錯病棟，不然就是我真的病太嚴重了這樣（￣▽￣）過去人生其實算很常跑醫院的不健康寶寶，但看到這樣另類的醫院裝潢還真是頭一遭，而且原本以為這可能是歐美國家才會這麼幽默，沒想到～竟然在日本！！位在東京江戶川旁的江戶川病院，絕對能給你不同過去的就醫經驗喔（指）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaaXrg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaaXrg.jpg&h=5a803332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaaXrw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaaXrw.jpg&h=263b0219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n停車場牆上的壁畫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaSd.jpg&h=acd9b05c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醫院平面圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaSe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaSe.jpg&h=6073b0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaSWpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaSWpw.jpg&h=89c083cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅色主題病房<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaWWqA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaWWqA.jpg&h=6dc0bef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n輪椅圖案<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaSX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaSX.jpg&h=7ebbf66e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在大象的肚內做磁力共振<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaSY.jpg&h=b211f6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旁邊牆上的壁紙還是愛麗絲夢遊仙境<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaSZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaSZ.jpg&h=3c9ef113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaSa.jpg&h=e439be38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaSb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaSb.jpg&h=6ab6b9db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaSc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%2F68%2Fp6CVpqSclaSc.jpg&h=a61cb945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醫院走廊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2014/55/68/p6CVpqSclaWWqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2014%2F55%